1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 14=

3
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,280
Move.

4
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:15,599
Stop!

5
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,319
You don't seem surprised

6
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,079
to see me.

7
00:01:29,799 --> 00:01:31,079
You're like a haunting ghost.

8
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:33,599
If your lover could protect you,

9
00:01:33,799 --> 00:01:35,760
why would I need to haunt you?

10
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:36,519
Oh, and

11
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,239
he was about to hurt you just now.

12
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:41,000
How pitiful you are.

13
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:43,159
Your love misplaced.

14
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:44,640
He was being controlled.

15
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,040
It wasn't what he wanted.

16
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:49,400
If his feelings were true,

17
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,959
how could anyone control him?

18
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:55,040
But Consort Rong,

19
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,359
you left the palace without permission.

20
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,640
Aren't you afraid of
His Majesty's wrath?

21
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:01,439
Thanks to you,

22
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,519
I am here

23
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:04,280
on His Majesty's orders to capture you.

24
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,039
So

25
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:10,319
you're here to find His Majesty
a new favorite.

26
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:11,919
Makes sense.

27
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,479
Once I'm there,

28
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:15,479
you'll be cast aside.

29
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:18,680
You're nothing but a plaything.

30
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,639
You think you can shake my position?

31
00:02:22,479 --> 00:02:23,680
Besides,

32
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,360
what makes you think

33
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,159
I'd actually take you back?

34
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:29,800
While apprehending you,

35
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,639
you put up fierce resistance,

36
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,000
and my guards

37
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,879
accidentally killed you.

38
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:38,039
And I executed those guards for it.

39
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:39,479
How does

40
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:41,879
that story sound to you?

41
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,319
What's happening?

42
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:48,280
What?

43
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,000
Is the Divine Power

44
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,479
not working?

45
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:57,280
Lord Nine-Thousand can't help you now.

46
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:01,719
You've made me so angry.

47
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,120
Killing you with one stab

48
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:06,120
would be far too boring.

49
00:03:08,319 --> 00:03:09,919
Where should I strike

50
00:03:09,919 --> 00:03:12,080
with the first blow?

51
00:03:12,719 --> 00:03:14,039
What do you think?

52
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,240
(I trust you.)

53
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,479
Move.

54
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,240
Stop!

55
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,280
My Lord.

56
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,319
Holy Maiden.

57
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:00,960
My...

58
00:04:03,319 --> 00:04:03,800
My Lord.

59
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,680
You scared me to death!

60
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,599
You two were flying kites

61
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:06,759
for so long without coming back.

62
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:08,400
I thought something had happened.

63
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:09,400
So I

64
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,560
brought everyone here.

65
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,319
My Lord,

66
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:21,480
you're better?

67
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,560
We were just attacked

68
00:04:24,879 --> 00:04:25,600
by Rong Zhaohua's men.

69
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:25,959
Over there!

70
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:26,480
What?

71
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,199
Give me the sword.

72
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:27,600
Quickly!

73
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:29,279
My Lord.

74
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:29,720
After them!

75
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:30,600
You're wounded.

76
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:31,439
Follow me.

77
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:32,079
It's nothing.

78
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,199
Wait.

79
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,199
How about this?

80
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,000
Holy Maiden,

81
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,560
My Lord,

82
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:36,600
you two head back first.

83
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,680
Leave those scumbags

84
00:04:37,759 --> 00:04:38,600
to me.

85
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:39,920
Rest assured, My Lord.

86
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,240
I'll make sure

87
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,839
to leave at least one alive

88
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:43,920
for you to deal with.

89
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,199
Watch out.

90
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,759
Reporting to Your Majesty.

91
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,600
I was ambushed yesterday.

92
00:05:08,639 --> 00:05:09,759
Are you alright, my dear minister?

93
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:10,560
Let me see.

94
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:11,639
Just a scratch.

95
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:12,480
It'll heal in a few days.

96
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,680
Thank you for your concern.

97
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:15,000
Good to hear.

98
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,480
But

99
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:17,879
I truly wonder who

100
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:19,199
would do this to you.

101
00:05:19,519 --> 00:05:20,480
When I find out,

102
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,519
they will be severely punished.

103
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:25,879
Feng Liu.

104
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,480
Move.

105
00:05:30,399 --> 00:05:30,879
Kneel.

106
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,040
Your Majesty.

107
00:05:35,519 --> 00:05:36,000
My Lord.

108
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:37,399
Your Majesty.

109
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,920
This man is one
of yesterday's assassins.

110
00:05:41,959 --> 00:05:43,319
These men are trained warriors,

111
00:05:43,319 --> 00:05:44,759
raised from childhood

112
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,199
never to speak under any circumstances.

113
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:51,319
But if he were to face his master

114
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:52,839
in person,

115
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,639
the situation would be different.

116
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:14,120
Consort Rong.

117
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,240
His Majesty is here.

118
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:16,839
Understood.

119
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,680
You may leave.

120
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:24,160
Greetings, Your Majesty.

121
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,120
You're with child, my dear.

122
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:25,959
Please rise.

123
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:28,879
What brings Lord Nine-Thousand

124
00:06:28,879 --> 00:06:30,439
here today?

125
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:31,519
My dear.

126
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,079
Yesterday,

127
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:34,360
where were you?

128
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,000
I am with child,

129
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,800
so naturally,

130
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,079
I was in the palace.

131
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:39,879
Why does Your Majesty ask?

132
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,199
But my dear minister claims

133
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:43,399
he saw you outside the city yesterday,

134
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,160
with warriors,

135
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,839
attempting to assassinate him.

136
00:06:46,839 --> 00:06:49,680
I know you and my brother
were never on good terms,

137
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,839
but now that he's gone,

138
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:53,560
the past should be laid to rest.

139
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:54,920
I don't understand

140
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,439
why you still target me like this.

141
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:03,959
Kneel.

142
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,639
Do you think you can slander me

143
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:11,160
by dragging in any random man?

144
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,040
I haven't even spoken yet.

145
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:15,120
How do you know this man

146
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,000
is an assassin?

147
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:20,480
Do you recognize him?

148
00:07:21,199 --> 00:07:22,480
Bring him in.

149
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,120
What else could you be up to?

150
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,319
You're absolutely right.

151
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:28,480
This is a carefully trained warrior.

152
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,759
He would never easily confess
who sent him.

153
00:07:30,759 --> 00:07:32,800
Then what was that talk
about a confrontation?

154
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,639
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

155
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:37,319
I lied just now.

156
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:38,759
But I did it

157
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:41,639
to force a confrontation
with Consort Rong.

158
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,199
That day outside the city,

159
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:45,319
I wounded her on the wrist
with my sword.

160
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,199
She lives deep in the palace,

161
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:49,319
in comfort and ease.

162
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,879
How could she have a sword wound?

163
00:07:52,079 --> 00:07:53,519
So I ask Consort Rong

164
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,839
to show me her hand.

165
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:56,480
How dare you!

166
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,040
My hand,

167
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,680
how dare a eunuch like you
lay eyes on it?

168
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,160
You're right.

169
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,560
Since I'm a eunuch,

170
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,519
no different from a woman,

171
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,720
what's the harm in showing me?

172
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:06,000
But your reluctance

173
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:08,040
only makes it seem more true.

174
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,680
What if I refuse?

175
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,439
What then?

176
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,079
You insolent eunuch.

177
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,160
You...

178
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:26,639
Your Majesty.

179
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:29,360
My family is weak and powerless.

180
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,519
Does that mean
I can be bullied like this?

181
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:32,519
Feng Ye.

182
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,639
This matter,

183
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,399
you owe me an explanation.

184
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,440
I'm guilty, Your Majesty.

185
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,639
Please punish me.

186
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,320
My dear.

187
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,600
Feng Ye was likely

188
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:42,039
instigated by someone else.

189
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,759
Apologize to my consort now,

190
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:44,440
and this matter

191
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,080
will be settled.

192
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:48,360
Forgive me, Consort Rong.

193
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:49,720
Leave us now.

194
00:08:50,279 --> 00:08:51,000
I take my leave.

195
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:55,200
Go.

196
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:06,480
Your Majesty.

197
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,159
I failed to bring her back

198
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:10,919
and caused you trouble instead.

199
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:12,039
Please punish me.

200
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,200
I know your heart, my dear.

201
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,519
Jiang Yukui won't escape

202
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:17,080
my grasp.

203
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,759
But you put yourself in danger for me.

204
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:19,840
That breaks my heart.

205
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:21,000
What danger?

206
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,080
I'm perfectly fine.

207
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:23,960
My dear.

208
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,919
Why did Feng Ye claim

209
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,120
your wrist was wounded?

210
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,320
Let me see.

211
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:31,240
In the heat of the moment,

212
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,159
what he wounded

213
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:33,279
was my decoy.

214
00:09:35,279 --> 00:09:36,559
Since you're unharmed,

215
00:09:36,559 --> 00:09:37,399
I can

216
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,799
rest easy.

217
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,120
Strange.

218
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:58,960
My Lord

219
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,000
clearly wounded her,

220
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,759
so how did the wound disappear?

221
00:10:02,399 --> 00:10:03,879
Even if His Majesty
had miracle medicine,

222
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:06,159
it couldn't heal that fast.

223
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:08,879
Could Rong Zhaohua

224
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,240
also possess the Divine Power?

225
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:10,919
Impossible.

226
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:13,759
The Divine Power is only held
by the Holy Maiden of the Zhao Tribe.

227
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:15,799
That's certain.

228
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:17,039
Then Rong Zhaohua...

229
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,799
She's truly unfathomable.

230
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:22,840
Before,

231
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,799
I underestimated her.

232
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:39,879
My Lord,

233
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:40,960
let's not dwell on all this

234
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,440
for now.

235
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,159
I'm tired.

236
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:44,519
I'm going to rest now.

237
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:48,840
Look.

238
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,960
The moonlight is so beautiful tonight.

239
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,000
This fine evening,

240
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:52,879
this lovely view,

241
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,080
two lovebirds together.

242
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,559
My Lord and the Holy Maiden...

243
00:10:57,559 --> 00:10:58,320
Go back.

244
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:13,159
Before,

245
00:11:14,159 --> 00:11:15,799
when I went against your wishes

246
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,399
and forced you out of the palace.

247
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,080
The reason I did that

248
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:22,080
was that I didn't want to see
you get hurt.

249
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,879
I know.

250
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,080
And during this time,

251
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,559
I lost my mind.

252
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,360
Many of my actions

253
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,840
were beyond my control.

254
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:33,960
I never meant to hurt you.

255
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,639
Trust me.

256
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:38,420
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

257
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:42,120
What if I

258
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,360
were still angry?

259
00:11:43,980 --> 00:11:46,980
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

260
00:11:47,300 --> 00:11:50,100
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

261
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:51,240
Then I suppose

262
00:11:53,039 --> 00:11:55,039
I'll have to leave myself

263
00:11:55,039 --> 00:11:56,360
to your mercy.

264
00:11:57,580 --> 00:12:00,780
♪The green lamp sheds no light
upon one who entered the path♪

265
00:12:01,020 --> 00:12:04,140
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

266
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:05,159
It's getting late.

267
00:12:06,679 --> 00:12:07,559
Go rest.

268
00:12:07,820 --> 00:12:10,780
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

269
00:12:10,780 --> 00:12:14,260
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

270
00:12:14,260 --> 00:12:17,860
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

271
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:19,519
My Lord.

272
00:12:21,260 --> 00:12:23,060
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪

273
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,720
You said before

274
00:12:25,879 --> 00:12:27,159
that you would help me take revenge.

275
00:12:27,919 --> 00:12:28,759
Was that

276
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,360
true?

277
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,519
Absolutely.

278
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,639
Good.

279
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,360
Okay, I trust you.

280
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:41,860
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

281
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:45,260
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

282
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:47,700
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

283
00:12:47,820 --> 00:12:51,700
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

284
00:12:52,300 --> 00:12:55,460
♪The green lamp sheds no light
upon one who entered the path♪

285
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:58,980
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

286
00:12:59,140 --> 00:13:02,380
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

287
00:13:02,380 --> 00:13:05,500
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪

288
00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:09,559
Zhaohua,

289
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,600
where are you taking me?

290
00:13:12,279 --> 00:13:13,679
Just wait a little longer,

291
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:15,600
Your Majesty. You'll see soon.

292
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:19,799
We're here.

293
00:13:50,180 --> 00:13:51,580
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

294
00:13:52,060 --> 00:13:53,500
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

295
00:13:53,700 --> 00:13:56,820
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

296
00:13:57,140 --> 00:14:00,940
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

297
00:14:03,900 --> 00:14:05,620
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

298
00:14:05,620 --> 00:14:07,140
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

299
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:10,900
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

300
00:14:10,900 --> 00:14:14,900
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

301
00:14:16,060 --> 00:14:19,220
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

302
00:14:19,220 --> 00:14:22,780
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

303
00:14:22,780 --> 00:14:25,100
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

304
00:14:25,100 --> 00:14:29,300
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

305
00:14:29,740 --> 00:14:31,380
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

306
00:14:31,380 --> 00:14:32,900
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

307
00:14:32,900 --> 00:14:36,100
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

308
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:38,420
♪In dreams, it's you♪

309
00:14:38,420 --> 00:14:39,820
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

310
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:43,140
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

311
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:46,540
♪I can't forget the stars in your eyes♪

312
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:50,100
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

313
00:14:50,100 --> 00:14:53,340
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

314
00:14:53,340 --> 00:14:56,780
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
